data.revised_prompt: Create an abstract, digital art avatar icon. Visualize a warm, glowing orb positioned against a dark backdrop. The orb is imbued with the colors of amber and honey, interlaced with delicate internal patterns mimicking neural networks or light refracting through glass. The orb radiates a soft, warm light outwards, giving it a sense of being alive, attentive and present, in contrast to being cold or robotic. The design should be minimalist and devoid of any faces or text, making it suitable for use as a profile picture.
